  ('medical-tech-moex-20552', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-483fb9c7', 'sub-medical-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關競爭性抑制劑之敘述，何者錯誤？ 其結構常常與受質相仿    會增加K m 可以利用高濃度的受質來克服這種抑制  會增加反應的V max', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a26f56bc74e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "64bccf8e4022", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生物化學與臨床生化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 55, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20553', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-483fb9c7', 'sub-medical-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '利用Lineweaver-Burk圖所繪出之兩條直線，其一為有酵素抑制物，另一為無抑制物存在之狀況。若此兩條 直線既不交會於X軸上，也不交會於Y軸上，且互相平行。則此種抑制型式為： 競爭型（competitive inhibition）  非競爭型（non-competitive inhibition） 不競爭型（uncompetitive inhibition）  混合型（mixed inhibition）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a26f56bc74e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "64bccf8e4022", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生物化學與臨床生化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 56, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
